Sentencas: With the starch as pore-forming agent, the technology of making porous YSZ was determined including pore-forming agent content and proportions of tape casting slurry.
Titulo: Preparation of Cu-CeO2-YSZ anode by tape casting and impregnation for solid oxide fuel cell

Sentencas: Porous-YSZ/density-YSZ compound substrate with porous-YSZ support was obtained by compound tape casting.

Sentencas: Then, Pt as the cathode, the effects of porous-YSZ porosity and impregnation condition on anode performance was discussed through the charge characteristics of fuel cells.

Sentencas: The porosity of porous-YSZ could achieve to 70% after sintering for 6 h at 1500 degrees C, when pore former volume fractions was 65wt% in materials.
